QuestData.Title: Necessary Resourcing
QuestData.Description:
Devourers are consuming neomotes.
We need neomotes for necessary creation work. Without them, we are unable to complete our work.
Eliminate the devourers and retrieve the neomotes.
QuestData.LogDescription: Obtain $1oa Neomote Residue and $2oa Solidified Neomotes from Devourers in Zereth Mortis.
QuestData.RewardText: You have completed the task. Thank you for your assistance.
